00137 tommy_inline tommy_node* tommy_list_tail(tommy_list* list)
00138 {
00139         tommy_node* head = tommy_list_head(list);
00140 
00141         if (!head)
00142                 return 0;
00143 
00144         return head->prev;
00145 }

00152 tommy_inline void tommy_list_insert_first(tommy_list* list, tommy_node* node)
00153 {
00154         /* one element "circular" prev list */   
00155         node->prev = node;
00156 
00157         /* one element "0 terminated" next list */
00158         node->next = 0;
00159 
00160         *list = node;
00161 }
00162 
00169 tommy_inline void tommy_list_insert_head_not_empty(tommy_list* list, tommy_node* node)
00170 {
00171         tommy_node* head = tommy_list_head(list);
00172 
00173         /* insert in the "circular" prev list */
00174         node->prev = head->prev;
00175         head->prev = node;
00176 
00177         /* insert in the "0 terminated" next list */
00178         node->next = head;
00179 
00180         *list = node;
00181 }
00182 
00189 tommy_inline void tommy_list_insert_tail_not_empty(tommy_node* head, tommy_node* node)
00190 {
00191         /* insert in the "circular" prev list */
00192         node->prev = head->prev;
00193         head->prev = node;
00194 
00195         /* insert in the "0 terminated" next list */
00196         node->next = 0;
00197         node->prev->next = node;
00198 }

00205 tommy_inline void tommy_list_insert_head(tommy_list* list, tommy_node* node, void* data)
00206 {
00207         tommy_node* head = tommy_list_head(list);
00208 
00209         if (head) {
00210                 tommy_list_insert_head_not_empty(list, node);
00211         } else {
00212                 tommy_list_insert_first(list, node);
00213         }
00214 
00215         node->data = data;
00216 }

00223 tommy_inline void tommy_list_insert_tail(tommy_list* list, tommy_node* node, void* data)
00224 {
00225         tommy_node* head = tommy_list_head(list);
00226 
00227         if (head) {
00228                 tommy_list_insert_tail_not_empty(head, node);
00229         } else {
00230                 tommy_list_insert_first(list, node);
00231         }
00232 
00233         node->data = data;
00234 }

00241 tommy_inline tommy_node* tommy_list_remove_head_not_empty(tommy_list* list)
00242 {
00243         tommy_node* head = tommy_list_head(list);
00244 
00245         /* remove from the "circular" prev list */
00246         head->next->prev = head->prev;
00247 
00248         /* remove from the "0 terminated" next list */
00249         *list = head->next; /* the new head, in case 0 */
00250 
00251         return head;
00252 }
00253 
00262 tommy_inline void* tommy_list_remove_existing(tommy_list* list, tommy_node* node)
00263 {
00264         tommy_node* head = tommy_list_head(list);
00265 
00266         /* remove from the "circular" prev list */
00267         if (node->next) { 
00268                 node->next->prev = node->prev;
00269         } else {
00270                 head->prev = node->prev; /* the last */
00271         }
00272 
00273         /* remove from the "0 terminated" next list */
00274         if (head == node) {
00275                 *list = node->next; /* the new head, in case 0 */
00276         } else {
00277                 node->prev->next = node->next;
00278         }
00279 
00280         return node->data;
00281 }

00311 tommy_inline void tommy_list_foreach(tommy_list* list, tommy_foreach_func* func)
00312 {
00313         tommy_node* node = tommy_list_head(list);
00314         while (node) {
00315                 void* data = node->data;
00316                 node = node->next;
00317                 func(data);
00318         }
00319 }
